How to run program?


1. Run maven script for packing.
2. Following to the project path in the command line and use one of the command.


java -jar target/test-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar -d -s out.txt input1.txt input2.txt
java -jar target/test-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar -s  out.txt input1.txt input2.txt input3.txt
java -jar target/test-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar -i -a out.txt input2.txt

Where following parameters mean:
 -a and -d - sort mode - increase (default) or decreasing
 -s and -i - data type - strings or integers

Use JDK 1.8 version.